        <h2>About Rohanth's Blog</h2>

        <div class="about-content">
            <p>Welcome to Rohanth's Blog, a platform dedicated to sharing insightful and engaging blog posts. Our mission is to provide a space for individuals to express their thoughts, ideas, and experiences in a meaningful way.</p>

